title: Kin Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, Fast food, Take-out, English
description: Sample breakfast options include raw bircher muesli and not-blt sandwich (maple syrup/soya/hickory smoke marinated coconut on seeded sourdough with lettuce and tomatoes); and lunch include salads and a daily changing vegan special. Offers a selection of vegan muffins and cakes throughout the day (from local baker). Beverages include hot drinks, juices, espresso, filter coffee, tea, and soda. Almond milk and Bonsoy are available as milk alternatives. Has Wi-Fi.
